_sText:
GG_DEAGLE5_CUBEThis is my latest that I have made. I am very proud of it since I put a whole lot of work into it.
Special Thanks Here are some people that I want to thank for helping me make my map the best it can be.
  • Greyfrog - Thank you for helping me optimize and make the map look a lot cooler.
  • Crazypip666 - Thank you for instructing me where to place my func_details
  • Ownt -Thank you for giving me feedback on my map
  • HacksawJack - Thank you for making the custom logo for my map
  • My Studio - Thank you also for helping me and giving me feedback

Notes
  • I tired a lot of new things in this map. I used a lot of func_details, well more that I have in any previous map.
  • I used a new lighting technique and I think it looks great!
  • I used the skip texture for the first time and it turned out very well.
  • I made everything by hand and used made all of it up (except for the box layout) and I think it looks amazing.
  • I used a env_fog_controller for the first time (thanks to Greyfrog) and it gives the map a great effect.

What is included In the file i have included the Map file as well as a NAV file for bots.

How to installOnce you download the rar file, you should extract it to your cstrike folder. It will ask you if you want to replace the files. Click yes.

Random Info
  • The average compile time was about 16 minutes
  • The most frequent obscenity uttered was "fuck"
  • It took a total of 27 days to make this map
  • Greyfrog doesnt like when I talk about his wife
  • Nosoul likes ponies
Please! When you assess, please give me good, honest feed back and tell me what I can improve on!Thank you all,
Nosoul!
